PAT snooping

- only one PAT table in input session
- when PAT version change, will clean up input PID table and in program list,
  and restart snooping (same as session start).
- Out session PID table will be cleaned up and repopulated when the TP info
  with new_pat flag is processed.  Same to output PSI generation.


